All tasks complete. Here's a summary of what was implemented:

**US-008: Agent health watchdog**

- **`src/core/lock.ts`**: Extended lock file format to `<PID>\n<ISO timestamp>`. Added `updateHeartbeat()` function. Backward compatible with old PID-only format.
- **`src/core/watchdog.ts`** (new): `checkAgentHealth()` returns health states: `healthy`, `unresponsive` (heartbeat older than poll×3), `stuck` (checkpoint stale), `dead` (PID gone), `stopped` (no lock).
- **`src/core/polling.ts`**: Calls `updateHeartbeat()` at the start of every cycle.
- **`src/commands/status.ts`**: Shows health indicator in status table (`RUNNING (healthy)` vs `RUNNING (unresponsive?)`). Added `--watch` mode with `--interval` for continuous monitoring with desktop notifications on state changes.
- **`src/commands/completion.ts`**: Updated bash/zsh/fish completions for `--watch` and `--interval`.
- **Tests**: 12 new tests in `tests/core/watchdog.test.ts`, updated 1 existing lock test. All 166 tests pass.

